{"tid":2071978,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"姊妹淘，第二春 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-06-20T09:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T09:03:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a01faff7ad59284304921e97eaad0421fd3d9119","tid":2071978,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200620/20940616/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200620%2F20940616%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w%2FPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=5598d84b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200620%2F20940616%2F&h=49c42526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200620/20940616/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n姊妹淘，第二春 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200620/large/1592547157_0afb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200620%2Flarge%2F1592547157_0afb.jpg&h=2b0a0f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來。。。。。餘氣。<br />\n<br />\n不過有。。。。。政治第二春。」<br />\n<br />\n我倒不發覺。只見一貫的不敢正視傳媒、鏡頭，還不停眨眼，眨眨眨&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n──但，她也真的找到「第二春」。雖然港人懷念的白襪仔林手足波叔不知哪去了？波叔脫苦海有第二春才更值得恭喜呢。而毒娥之「春」是華春瑩。<br />\n<br />\n華大媽潑辣，鄭大媽陰毒，各擅勝場，本非一路，但無獨有偶，華大媽亦一眨眼專家，說到「中國才是假新聞的最大受害者」，還為新一波武肺疫情在北京爆發，甩鍋北歐三文魚（魚食死貓！）。祖國之正義、真實、公正、客觀，一如漆黑夜間的明亮燭光&hellip;&hellip;她又不停眨眨眨&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n毒娥原是台灣小英總統高票連任的推手，送中修例讓之欣然受惠登寶座，但小英眨眼速度未夠班。<br />\n<br />\n根據心理學，避正視、狂眨眼、摸鼻子、冒汗，都是說謊心虛下意識表現──不過兩大媽若是女同志，屬眉目傳情吧；若是間諜，不過打摩斯密碼，一如《風聲》中的姊妹淘。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}